p193
aVif you have a loaf of sliced bread in your house?
p194
aVWho lives in a household where that crust \u2014
p195
aVthat slice at the first and last end of each loaf \u2014
p196
aVwho lives in a household where it does get eaten?
p197
aVOkay, most people, not everyone, but most people,
p198
aVand this is, I'm glad to say, what I see across the world,
