aVand yet has anyone seen a supermarket or sandwich shop
p200
aVanywhere in the world that serves sandwiches
p201
aVwith crusts on it? (Laughter)
p202
aVI certainly haven't.
p203
aVSo I kept on thinking, where do those crusts go? (Laughter)
