aVIn the same year that I visited this factory,
p208
aVI went to Pakistan, where people in 2008 were going hungry
p209
aVas a result of a squeeze on global food supplies.
p210
aVWe contribute to that squeeze
p211
aVby depositing food in bins here in Britain
p212
